Vrittikut Ashram is a unique ashram of Vihangam Yoga, situated in village Pakadi of Balia district in U.P, India. It is also the birth place of Sri Sadguru Sadafaldeoji Maharaj. It is full of green environment surrounded with natural ponds.It is the main focal point of the Ashram, where on meditation, people can feel the spiritual vibration and practical experiences within them. Here Sri Sadguru Sadafaldeoji Maharaj himself has practiced meditation. It is a five floored construction, indicating the five steps of Vihangam Yoga, with a lotus structure at the top.We believe that you deserve to have a hassle-free banking experience with HDFC Bank.
